Package imp.core.exceptions.parser

Contains IMP exceptions specific to the parser.

See: Description

    Class Description
    TestIncorrectNumberOfPoints
    Test class intended to test the exception thrown when there is an incorrect number of points
    TestModelVariableAlreadyExists
    Test class intended to test the exception thrown when a model variable already exists
    TestModelVariableDoesNotExist
    Test class intended to test the exception thrown when a model variable is requested but does not exist
    TestParserException
    Tests the abstract parser exception
    TestTooManyPointsInDataStatement
    Test class intended to test the exception thrown when a data statement contains too many points
